text.jpText:
『ウマネイル☆ちゃんねる』のライブ配信
マジ神テク連発で神ってたわ～～♪
text.enText:
The live broadcast of "Umaneil☆Channel" was a 
series of seriously divine techniques that 
were divine～～～!

text.jpText:
けどグラデの作り方とか聞いたら、
神すぎて逆に凹んだっていう……。
ポリッシュ使いえぐいて。
text.enText:
But when I asked her how to make a gradient, 
she said it was so godly that it made 
her depressed.…… I was so impressed 
with her use of polishes.

text.jpText:
……でもまぁ、悩んだら負けだし？
神テク盗むしかないっしょ♪
text.enText:
…… but well, if you're worried about 
it, you'll lose, right? You have 
to steal God's technique.

text.jpText:
とりま神サロン行くしかないわ！
……場所知らんけど！！
text.enText:
At least I'll have to go to the God Salon! I 
don't know where…… is!
